That does not sound like an actual beep.  Atleast how I am hearing  it.  I do 
hear a voice in the background but cannot make out what it is  saying.  
Almost as if someone is trying to make that noise for you.
 
Jeff

Testing #32, an it periodically gets some kind of feed back, maybe from a  
bad connection, but as the recording progresses there's something actually  
saying 'Beep' in the squawks. I copied them all the one file.  

Frank-S
